    		<div class="w3-center">
      			<h2>About Multus</h2>
      			<p>
      				Multus is an app designed to help students beat procrastination and increase productivity in a fun and enjoyable way.
      			</p> <br>
      			<h2>Task Page</h2>
      			<p>
      				On this page you can view your current tasks, create new tasks, or view more information on your current tasks. Create a new task by pressing the + button, and to edit, delete, or view the description of a task, press the task name.
      			</p> <br>
      			<h2>Profile</h2>
      			<p>
      				On this page you can view your profile, as well as your statistics such as your streak days, tasks completed, and hours logged. Here, you can also view challenges you have completed, as well as upcoming challenges to complete.
      			</p> <br>
      			<h2>Past Tasks</h2>
      			<p>
      				On this page you can view your past tasks that you have completed. You are able to edit or delete these tasks as well. <!-- You can also search by key words, or order them using different methods. -->
      			</p>
    		</div>
